For additional context about technologies to be used, project structure,
shell commands, and other important information, read the current plan at
`specs/012-monthly-budget-manager/plan.md` and the developer quickstart at
`specs/012-monthly-budget-manager/quickstart.md`.

Primary local dev workflow: `python local_run.py --text "..."` or
`python local_run.py --image path/to/receipt.jpg` (requires GEMINI_API_KEY only;
add SUPABASE_URL + SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY to persist expenses and LLM usage metering).

Web dashboard (feature 009): `cd web && npm install && npm run dev` — see
`specs/009-expense-web-dashboard/quickstart.md` for LINE Login, LIFF, and Vercel setup.

Reply-edit testing: log an expense, note `bot_message_id`, then
`python local_run.py --reply-to <bot_message_id> --text "3800円"`.

Group usage / pooling: `python local_run.py --group-id <group_id> --text "..."`

Supabase project: `https://nyuenufldaqsjybjhawl.supabase.co`
